name: wmf-e3-editor-milestones
notes:
Files in 1K_editors.zip:

metrics_1K_test_it2.2_editcounts.tsv - edit counts, main namespace (0) and User Talk (3) for test group users after making their 1000th edit

metrics_1K_control_it2.2_editcounts.tsv - edit counts, main namespace (0) and User Talk (3) for control group users after making their 1000th edit	

metrics_1K_bstar_test_it2.2_editcounts.tsv - edit counts, main namespace (0) and User Talk (3) for test group users after receiving the barnstar for the 1000th edit

metrics_1K_bstar_test_it2.2_editcounts_all.tsv - edit counts, all namespaces for test group users after receiving the barnstar for the 1000th edit

metrics_1K_control_it2.2_editcounts_all.tsv - edit counts, all namespaces for control group users after making their 1000th edit

metrics_1K_test_it2.2_editcounts_all.tsv - edit counts, all namespaces for test group users after making their 1000th edit

Description of metrics:

recipient_name - user name

timestamp - time of event (e.g. 1000th edit, barnstar receipt) 

ns_0_revisions_before - edits in namespace 0 by user before event

ns_0_revisions_after_0_3 - edits in namespace 0 by user 0-3 days after event	

ns_3_revisions_before -  edits in namespace 3 by user before event

ns_3_revisions_after_0_3 - edits in namespace 3 by user 0-3 days after event

revisions_before -	edits in all namespaces by user before event

revisions_before_3_0 - edits in all namespaces by user 0-3 days before event

revisions_after_0_3 - edits in all namespaces by user 0-3 days after event	

revisions_after_3_30 - edits in all namespaces by user 3-30 days after event

revisions_after_gt_30 - edits in all namespaces by user greater than 30 days after event
title: WMF E3 Editor Milestones
